    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, you can spend 10 chakra to activate your latent Bestial Transformation. This form lasts up to 1 minute. While it is active: Increase both your speed and jump distance by 10 feet. You can climb surfaces, walls, and water walk without any movement penalty, and ignore difficult terrain. You gain advantage on checks that rely on hearing or smell.</p>",
